Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:10 LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的事实 就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音…玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何我会变成真神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所认定的神绝对不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白肉体是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死的意思 只是把肉体放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说千砂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（这种地方 我不存在也没所谓）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说也对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让网络协议进化的更趋完整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你的确做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但协议也只是协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已在更高层次之处加上我才知道的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把情报放在那资料里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎样的情报呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括我和那英利政美的思想 履历 记录 情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做到底有何意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以匿名的方式存在于网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能永远生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能控制网上的数据 支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种存在方式 应该称呼为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实神是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是能以普通的方式存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在上位的话 也不能称为神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 是被做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不再需要肉体了 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 把书收进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何突然变成如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做错过什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直不敢胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但果然还是变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我真的不该拥有肉体？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这现实世界已不再需要有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你道别了 玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的工作已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在短短的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没好好对待你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 其实从开始你就自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不能跟你说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真的喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有一般家庭的融洽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但曾是玲音父亲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也感到非常光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你不只是一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你到网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有人来欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该是这样子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要做什么？玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的世界 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是否做了个假的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据东方传说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士团的起源似乎是圆桌骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在还没有互联网时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们利用人与人之间所构成的网络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来收集所需要的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要做什么？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS…KNIGHTS到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想知道吗？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为作为计算机网络上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定要拥有崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到别的地方好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得这很无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 要不要来我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌幸你不来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太郎不会跟你这种小鬼玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么话 你也是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩年轻是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太郎 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网络新闻说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说名单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么名单？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS成员的名单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在网络上流传
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我替他注射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个换妈妈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快来的话我就继续玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈你好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要继续玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天世界各地出现连串自杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各地警方正全力追查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自杀身亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据消息报道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是网络上一个名叫KNIGHTS的组织之中的成员…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为何要这样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是我们客户的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把全世界的KNIGHTS成员找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就负责一切善后工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网上世界并非特别的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量只是真实世界的某部分备案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你在网上已全无存在目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正已平安无事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得你像是有守护神在保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天那英利政美残留的计算机程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要它从网络上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那位顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要我们将那程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远消失在网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…不需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 无论现实或网上都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法了解你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说是很不可思议的…感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些崇拜的人已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么照你所说的 神已经不存在了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是所有人都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有一个崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就还是能当神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌啊 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能以你所存在 都是我的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本就是网络的创造者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是网上的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网络童话的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界的岩仓玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个程序
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类所做出来的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没有一个实体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假的家人 假的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的玲音 已经是孤单一人
